casebody.data:
Michelle PIMIENTA, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
David ROSENFELD, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1864 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 13, 2018 SUAREZ, LOGUE and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon consideration, petitioner's emergency motion to stay lower court proceedings pending a decision on the petitioner's emergency petition for writ of prohibition is hereby denied.

Following review of the emergency petition for writ of prohibition, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
